def interpret_expression(self, expr, local_vars, allow_recursion):
    expr = expr.strip()

    if expr == '':  # Empty expression
        return None

    match = re.match(r'^(?P<func>%s)\((?P<args>[^()]+)?\)$' % _NAME_RE, expr)

        args = match.group('args')

        # check if the function is defined
